  {
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Nice find @ethanndickson! The path collision is very mind boggling since it should be unique on both t.TempDir and tt.path. It\u2019d be interesting to know the exact cause but just disabling parallel seems like the best option for now \ud83d\udc4d",
